3 Application Layer
=====================

Server/Client Structure

RESTful APIs:

http://localhost/ttt/1.0/name                              ['GET', 'PUT']
http://localhost/ttt/1.0/friends                           ['GET']
http://localhost/ttt/1.0/friend/<friend_name>              ['GET', 'POST']
http://localhost/ttt/1.0/friend/commands/<friend_name>     ['GET']

http://localhost/ttt/1.0/friend/command/alias/             ['PUT']
data: {"friend":"<name>","command":{"name":"<cmd_name>","alias":"<alias>"}}



